      "body" : "Tested ACK fa6a59dd397e62e850fc57df05cd6d117fbdcd82.\r\nThis is a quick and stable workaround and we should backport this to 0.12.\r\n**For 0.13 we need a better solution.**\r\n\r\nCurrent Master (to small on windows):\r\n<img width=\"620\" alt=\"bildschirmfoto 2016-01-22 um 09 39 07\" src=\"https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/178464/12506086/a30392a0-c0ec-11e5-979e-04377b914084.png\">\r\n\r\nCurrent 0.11 version, non pretty, non mono (people are use to this font size):\r\n<img width=\"670\" alt=\"bildschirmfoto 2016-01-22 um 09 41 02\" src=\"https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/178464/12506093/b067969e-c0ec-11e5-90ac-2daf36261565.png\">\r\n\r\nThis PR:\r\n<img width=\"612\" alt=\"bildschirmfoto 2016-01-22 um 09 38 12\" src=\"https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/178464/12506098/bd7b481c-c0ec-11e5-941a-abb18f8d5f97.png\">",
